criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  visceral obesity and at least two of other components: raised fasting serum glucose or
             known diabetes type 2; raised fasting serum triglycerides; raised fasting serum
             cholesterol; raised fasting serum LDL and low fasting serum HDL; high blood pressure,
             more than 130/85 mmHg.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  planned invasive procedure or surgery (whole body);

          -  planned surgery in mouth cavity;

          -  weakened immune system or taking immunosuppressives;

          -  diagnosed inflammatory bowel disease;

          -  known or diagnosed lactose intolerance.
